--- ncurses-6.1-20190623+/NEWS	2019-06-23 21:18:23.000000000 +0000
+++ ncurses-6.1-20190630/NEWS	2019-06-30 10:45:10.000000000 +0000
@@ -25,7 +25,7 @@
